en.home.hiw_title="From scan to signed report in four steps";
en.home.hiw_sub="ScanGuru drops into your existing workflow — upload directly or integrate over your PACS, and every study comes back as an explainable, dual-language report for clinician sign-off.";
en.home.hiw_s1t="Connect";
en.home.hiw_s1d="Upload through the web app, or integrate over DICOM/PACS and the REST API at api.scanguru.net.";
en.home.hiw_s2t="AI analysis";
en.home.hiw_s2d="Heterogeneous model ensembles analyze the study across 13+ trained models, with explainable attention heatmaps.";
en.home.hiw_s3t="Dual-language report";
en.home.hiw_s3d="A structured PDF in any of 83 languages — clinical, comprehensive, and patient variants, native language alongside English.";
en.home.hiw_s4t="Clinician review";
en.home.hiw_s4d="Results support a qualified clinician’s read, confirmed before any decision.";
en.home.hiw_s5t="Secure handling";
en.home.hiw_s5d="Encrypted in transit and at rest, with PHI-aware logging and role-based access. Data location and retention are agreed with each pilot partner.";
